==Cantonese==
===Etymology===
*[[親]] root meaning: blood relation
*:figurative meaning: to cause others to feel as if they are relatives, to be close to
*[[切]] root meaning: to cut
*:figurative meaning: to be close (as a knife is to flesh when it cuts)
